column5: Hi Y'all,  Me again.  Just finished a post about catching some decent size walleye , and my attemps to catch one bigger than 18" yesterday. Well i could not manage it yesterday, but after the post, went for a quick couple of casts from the yard...and wallop.....this guy just over 21". About time too....as the bigger walleye have been illusive for a couple of weeks now.   ONE MORE FOR TEAM#4
Hey Limey. I bet if you start calling them fish pickerel, you catch BIGGER ones.
Woohoo, more inches for Team 4.  Way to go Limeyangler  Joey
